@(A.28.8.10 = 10)  @note{cf. @xref[t.6.1.01,t.6.1.01.104]{6.1.01.104}, @xref[t.6.1.11,t.6.1.11.54]{6.1.11.54}, @xref[t.6.1.15,t.6.1.15.c3]{6.1.15.c3}, @xref[t.6.1.26,t.6.1.26.b4]{6.1.26.b4}} If oil is poured into the inside of a sceptre @note{-- nobody will know}.

